'''''Fars''''' or '''''Al-Montabaaho-fil-Fars''''' (Persian:المنطبعه فی القارس) is an [[Iran]]ian [[newspaper]]  in [[Fars Province|Fars]] region. The [[concessionaire]] of this magazine was ''Mirza Taghikhan Kashani'' and it was published in [[Shiraz]] since 1872. This was the first modern newspaper which was published in southern Iran.<ref>Rumi, Siroos, ''List of printed matters of Fars'' (2006); [[Ministry of Culture and Islamic Guidance (Iran)]]</ref>

